ore":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"咁問得已經有責任過好多棄養撚"},{"pid":"a0a3d692b3b3de03a7b9d0ad856fa7deac63d953","tid":1330402,"uid":109416,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"抑鬱養寵物好似可以減輕病情<br />\n<br />\n先唔好諗定日後事先。 諗現在<br />\n<br />\n無人知自己死期係幾時，每個人養寵物前都擔中會短命過隻寵物咁全世界都唔洗養啦<br />\n<br />\n但我建議你領養好過買。"},{"pid":"ee29c7777b7bdd5cbb10486a335de468554d5a8d","tid":1330402,"uid":152528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:22:07.000Z","msg":"養寵物可治療心靈"},{"pid":"f38ca086d99c5057982dea0ac9f8008f7597b506","tid":1330402,"uid":136039,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:17:27.000Z","msg":"好多虐貓既人都有抑鬱"},{"pid":"875b8263951292ea283718bc18b9be08434f1a64","tid":1330402,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"樓主想養咩寵物 ?"},{"pid":"fa7a5d251909b8b9f0967935ad585804ceb5f925","tid":1330402,"uid":265447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47b9aa28a3582ced8aa872c1afa3ed1dd110ea21","tid":1330402,"uid":180390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"自己一個住？"},{"pid":"da4df44e61f91881fdfefc68fb90d4fee1a1db24","tid":1330402,"uid":4943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"有能力同時間就養啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n領養左幾隻衰貓一年幾，如果無左佢地一定無依家咁開心"},{"pid":"ffabc594e04bf6f7dec6cf937a81439f3fa36ef3","tid":1330402,"uid":171523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6e7701bce7c4259e36675e396f437fabf39829d","tid":1330402,"uid":25960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"好驚突然有一日頂唔順 死左冇人照顧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又想寵物陪下自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:29:57.000Z","msg":"真，成日都想可以攬住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6d2f8c7819dfed5840b83392804ac930843b6a","tid":1330402,"uid":282909,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:33:31.000Z","msg":"同路人話你知<br />\n我以前唔敢養係好驚佢會離開我<br />\n但佢依家成為左我生命中嘅重心<br />\n佢嘅世界剩係得我呢個感覺<br />\n係支撐我每日行落去嘅動力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就3年啦 最近開始減到藥<br />\n我好多謝佢出現係我生命"},{"pid":"5f8c5999f5a1a9d5c532539f1bd3ed032c553809","tid":1330402,"uid":289751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:36:00.000Z","msg":"收養好啦，唔好買呀，竉物店做好多仆街野。"},{"pid":"8e7e3acdacc5ba72adfe3ee124d82d6df6282ffb","tid":1330402,"uid":118041,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:54:10.000Z","msg":"個人經歷<br />\n抑鬱+自卑咗五年，直到遇上一隻性格好似我，好孤單既一隻雪橇狗女，慢慢同佢接觸，建立信任，再領養佢，我終於走返出來。<br />\n點知養咗唔夠一年佢就有肝癌走咗，我將佢既大愛延續，做義工幫其他雪橇狗，而家個人都開朗咗，有寄託"},{"pid":"80c83ae81c20cc0d8600aeb765112966ae8af619","tid":1330402,"uid":167254,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"我有抑鬱10年，係狗狗日日比歡笑我，令我開始慢慢好返的。<br />\n當然，養狗之前梗係要諗下自己照唔照顧琴佢啦。"},{"pid":"7dc9803da25ed551f0d97ebc3fcbaaf08e3ccef6","tid":1330402,"uid":299372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"抑鬱 係連登領養既貓b<br />\n養左幾年<br />\n講真唔開心時吸下貓真係感到好抒壓<br />\n好感激遇上佢&hellip;&hellip;帶比我好大安慰<br />\n<br />\n更加難想像十幾年後冇左佢會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a2820b5d3b51b9df970f19037be95e60a4333d","tid":1330402,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d6d2f8c7819dfed5840b83392804ac930843b6a","tid":1330402,"uid":282909,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:33:31.000Z","msg":"同路人話你知<br />\n我以前唔敢養係好驚佢會離開我<br />\n但佢依家成為左我生命中嘅重心<br />\n佢嘅世界剩係得我呢個感覺<br />\n係支撐我每日行落去嘅動力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就3年啦 最近開始減到藥<br />\n我好多謝佢出現係我生命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多同路人陪你一齊走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6441e83f947e77d9971fd27be20226582434451","tid":1330402,"uid":264455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:06:12.000Z","msg":"只要承諾會一世好好照顧佢 抑鬱唔係大問題<br />\n一直都覺得自己同隻貓係互相照顧 只係唔同形式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e579d8d3b5f368b290b8b9ab70a8169ad36796","tid":1330402,"uid":60500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:17:04.000Z","msg":"唔好拎寵物出氣就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e336189f9fc3a5bfcb683382c585568bd1dc0446","tid":1330402,"uid":186323,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f4e579d8d3b5f368b290b8b9ab70a8169ad36796","tid":1330402,"uid":60500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:17:04.000Z","msg":"唔好拎寵物出氣就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"自卑嘅人打貓會感到有權威 會有快感"}]}